Semantic versioning: Every Capability carries CAPABILITY_VERSION and MINIMUM_CLIENT_VERSION.
Deprecation policy: 12 months notice before removal of any Contract method.
Migration path: Published before old version is removed; migration guide linked in Evolution Envelope.
Breaking changes: Increment MAJOR version. All breaking changes are announced in the changelog.
Backward compatibility: MINOR and PATCH changes are backward-compatible.
User agent plugins: Must declare min_octopussy_version in plugin.json. Incompatible plugins are rejected at load time with a clear error.


