D-06 — OCTOPUSSYMESSAGE — STRUCTURE &amp; PROCESSING CHAIN

Spec ref: §4.0.2 — OctopussyMessage; §8 — Messaging Architecture
Purpose: Defines the immutable message type that is the ONLY communication vehicle in the system. Shows all fields and the complete processing chain every message passes through.

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    OctopussyMessage  (frozen=True, slots=True)              │
│                    octopussy/core/message.py                                │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Field          Type              Description                               │
│  ─────────────  ────────────────  ────────────────────────────────────────  │
│  message_id     UUID              Unique message identifier (uuid4)         │
│  sender_id      UUID              Agent UUID of sender                      │
│  recipient_id   UUID              Agent UUID of recipient                   │
│  message_type   MessageType       TASK | RESULT | CONTROL | EVENT           │
│  payload        dict              JSON-serializable values only             │
│  priority       MessagePriority   CRITICAL=0 | HIGH=1 | NORMAL=2 | LOW=3   │
│  trace_id       UUID              Distributed tracing correlation ID        │
│  created_at     float             Unix timestamp UTC (time.time())          │
│  ttl_seconds    int               Time-to-live in seconds (default: 300)    │
│  signature      bytes             HMAC-SHA256 — MANDATORY, never Optional   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Factory Method: OctopussyMessage.create(sender_id, recipient_id,          │
│                    message_type, payload, secret: bytes, ...)               │
│  Verification:   message.verify_signature(secret: bytes) → bool            │
│                  (constant-time via hmac.compare_digest; never raises)      │
│  Expiry check:   message.is_expired() → bool                               │
│                  (time.time() > created_at + ttl_seconds)                   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

HMAC SIGNATURE COMPUTATION:
  sig_data = f"{message_id}{sender_id}{recipient_id}{message_type}
               {created_at}{ttl_seconds}{priority}".encode("utf-8")
  signature = hmac.new(secret, sig_data, hashlib.sha256).digest()

MESSAGE PROCESSING CHAIN (Chain of Responsibility in _message_loop):
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  Inbound OctopussyMessage arrives in inQ
              │
              ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  STEP 1: verify_signature(secret)   │──── FAIL ──► DROP + log warning
  └─────────────────────────────────────┘
              │ PASS
              ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  STEP 2: is_expired()               │──── EXPIRED ► DROP + log warning
  └─────────────────────────────────────┘
              │ NOT EXPIRED
              ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  STEP 3: message_type == CONTROL?   │──── YES ──► _handle_control(message)
  └─────────────────────────────────────┘
              │ NO (TASK / EVENT)
              ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  STEP 4: scan_prompt(payload)       │──── INJECTION ► DROP + audit log
  │          (SecurityPort)             │
  └─────────────────────────────────────┘
              │ CLEAN
              ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  STEP 5: check_budget(agent_id)     │──── EXHAUSTED ► DROP + notify sender
  │          (TokenBudgetPort)          │
  └─────────────────────────────────────┘
