    │                                  trace_id, spec, iteration); NOT shared between agents
    │
    ├── INJECTED PORTS (via inject_dependency() / AgentFactory at creation)
    │   ├── _llm_port        LLMPort              ◄── from LLMRouterCapability
    │   ├── _vlm_port        VLMPort | None        ◄── from LLMRouterCapability (if vlm_enabled)
