    │   ├── _security_port   SecurityPort          ◄── from SecurityCapability
    │   ├── _messaging       MessagingContract     ◄── from MessagingCapability
    │   ├── _lifecycle       AgentLifecyclePort    ◄── from AgentLifecycleManagerCapability
    │   └── _obs_port        ObservabilityPort     ◄── from ObservabilityCapability
    │
