    │   ├── LLMPortAdapter    — wraps LLMPort with Circuit Breaker + Retry+Backoff
    │   ├── VLMPortAdapter    — wraps VLMPort with Circuit Breaker + Retry+Backoff
    │   ├── MCPClientAdapter  — MCP 2025-11-25 Streamable HTTP client for all tool calls
    │   └── StateStore        — persists agent state to SQLite
    │
    └── SPEC (AgentSpec — frozen dataclass, immutable)
        ├── agent_id, name, description, agent_type, execution_mode
