  INVARIANTS:
  • Agents NEVER communicate via direct method calls — only OctopussyMessage
  • Agents NEVER share state with other agents
  • Agents NEVER block the event loop (all methods are async def)
  • Agents ALWAYS verify inbound message signature before processing
  • Agents ALWAYS check TTL before processing
  • Agents ALWAYS check token budget before every LLM call
  • Agents ALWAYS emit heartbeat every 30 seconds
  • Agents ALWAYS respect LoopGuard iteration ceiling


